'''新會商會港青基信學校'''（英語：San Wui Commercial Society YMCA of Hong Kong Christian School），缩写为'''SWYHKCS'''，是一所位于[[香港|香港]][[九龍|九龍]][[深水埗|深水埗]]的[[混合性別教育|男女]][[英语|英语]][[独立学校|私立]][[小学|小学]] <ref name="edb">{{Cite web|title=School Search|url=https://applications.edb.gov.hk/schoolsearch/schoolinfo.aspx?langno=1&scrn=592188000123|accessdate=9 May 2020|work=[[教育局_(香港)|教育局]]|archive-date=2020-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711235538/https://applications.edb.gov.hk/schoolsearch/schoolinfo.aspx?langno=1&scrn=592188000123|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=【小學概覽2019】全港直私小學學費表　男拔附小英華維持學費不變|date=4 September 2019|work=[[香港01|香港01]]|url=https://www.hk01.com/親子/371354/小學概覽2019-全港直私小學學費表-男拔附小英華維持學費不變|accessdate=9 May 2020|archive-date=2020-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200412160317/https://www.hk01.com/%E8%A6%AA%E5%AD%90/371354/%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E6%A6%82%E8%A6%BD2019-%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E7%9B%B4%E7%A7%81%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E5%AD%B8%E8%B2%BB%E8%A1%A8-%E7%94%B7%E6%8B%94%E9%99%84%E5%B0%8F%E8%8B%B1%E8%8F%AF%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E5%AD%B8%E8%B2%BB%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%8A|dead-url=no}}</ref>，這是僑港新會商會和[[香港基督教青年會|香港基督教青年會]]於2013年開辦的小學。<ref name="Ys201909">{{Cite web|title=Y’s Voices September 2019 Page 3|url=http://www.ymcahk.org.hk/main/filemanager/en/content_113/Ys201909.pdf|accessdate=9 May 2020|work=[[香港基督教青年會|香港基督教青年會]]|archive-date=2020-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200412160315/http://www.ymcahk.org.hk/main/filemanager/en/content_113/Ys201909.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

該校提供[[汉语|中文]]和[[数学教育|数学]]的本地课程、[[英语|英语]]和[[理工科|STEM]]学科的国际课程<ref name="curriculum">{{Cite web|title=School Curriculum|url=https://www.cs.edu.hk/curriculum.html|accessdate=9 May 2020|work=新會商會港青基信學校|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804232941/https://www.cs.edu.hk/curriculum.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、以及與[[英国教育|英国教育]]相對應的實踐邊做邊學（Learn by doing）。<ref name="mp20190501">{{Cite book|last=|title=OpenSchool|date=May 2019|publisher=[[明報|明報]]|page=52-55|quote=|url=https://www.openschool.hk/ebook/OpenSchool教育特刊-認清資優教育意義.pdf?fbclid=IwAR0oHTLtwTR0TKdMN3S4CP4H_ui_uKzgVstCMKmD1qI_ytPFp6LKAfs6ZHk|accessdate=9 May 2020|archive-date=2020-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413012618/https://www.openschool.hk/ebook/OpenSchool%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%2588%258A-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%25B8%2585%25E8%25B3%2587%25E5%2584%25AA%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E6%2584%258F%25E7%25BE%25A9.pdf%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0oHTLtwTR0TKdMN3S4CP4H_ui_uKzgVstCMKmD1qI_ytPFp6LKAfs6ZHk|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

